            <lg xml:id="TK1155">
<l>ōmpi ṉamaintār pirivōmpal maṟṟavar </l>
<l>nīṅki ṉaritāṟ puṇarvu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you would save (my life), delay the departure of my destined (husband); for if he departs, intercourse will become impossible.</l>
